name: Maureen Wilson
description:
I enjoy meals out or in, ambling in beautiful countryside, the theater and cinema. I try to stay fit and healthy but I am not fanatical.Love hanging out with friends and loved ones.
I am looking for a serious mature man to settle down with. If things go well then we can quickly be married. I need someone who is real, honest, truthful, loving, caring and romantic, mature.I am looking for my soul mate one more time. A best friend and lover. A honest caring loving man. For long term sexual serious relationship for my husband. I don’t have any kid and I am Looking for someone who is a loving, caring, and sharing person. Not afraid to express their opinions and being sensitive to mine.
I want someone who has a good personality, friendly, outgoing, confident with himself, Someone who is polite and respectful(to himself and others).Someone who respects me,and recognizes what a special person I am and treats me accordingly. I am looking for someone who will spend the rest of his life with me.
